    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Adding `Projectile: Bullet` to `HMG_muzzle:`/`HMGo_muzzle:` in \"/mods/d2k/smallguns.yaml\" fixes this bug for me ... so it looks like this:\r\n```yaml\r\nHMG_muzzle:\r\n\tReloadDelay: 16\r\n\tRange: 3c0\r\n\tProjectile: Bullet\r\n\tBurst: 3\r\n\tBurstDelay: 2\r\n\tWarhead@TargetValidation: SpreadDamage\r\n```\r\nTook me quite some time to narrow it down to this and I'm not using C#, so reading the trait-files didn't really help but maybe `Projectile:` is needed to trigger the muzzle sequence?!\r\n\r\nMaybe this can also be squeezed into #12515..."
  },
